{"tid":2253865,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"淺談死海古卷（Dead Sea Scrolls）","createTime":"2020-10-22T12:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T16:58:31.000Z","uid":44209,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d4301b00e552e46dae17aa5a10e339fd4427c63d","tid":2253865,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GdQ1Xx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GdQ1Xx.jpg&h=84503d5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n淺談死海古卷（Dead Sea Scrolls）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wYwvhv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwYwvhv5.jpg&h=9ee2c3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺1946年底或者1947年初嘅冬天，有幾個貝都因（Bedouin）嘅牧羊人喺死海西北面曠野嘅山坡放羊，其中一個細路掟石頭嗰陣意外打爛喺一個洞穴入面嘅缸瓦，啲貝都因人喺嗰度發現一啲古卷，再加上後來考古學家嘅發掘，就搵到依家我哋所俗稱嘅「死海古卷」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmcBXwp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmcBXwp.png&h=9dc1701f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n存放死海古卷嘅洞穴地理上同昆蘭遺址（Qumran）距離好接近，所以嗰啲洞穴我哋叫做昆蘭洞穴。原本有11個，但係喺2017年1月，昆蘭12號洞穴被發現（即係一共有12個洞穴）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DXTxvRv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDXTxvRv.jpg&h=e872fed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過第12號洞穴得啲缸瓦嘅碎片同埋一卷空白嘅皮卷，考古學家推論洞穴可能曾經有收藏文獻，但係俾人偷咗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PpaG8Dp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPpaG8Dp.jpg&h=d0cf2e9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n死海古卷嘅書寫語言主要係希伯來文，其次係亞蘭文，另外有少數嘅希臘文。成書年份係由公元前250年至公元68年。總數大約有九百份抄本，合共來自一萬多份殘片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGR7jLf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGR7jLf.jpg&h=bb9b37b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被發現嘅文獻種類有好多，但可以簡單分成兩大類：「聖經文獻」同「經外文獻」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjH6AiN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjH6AiN.jpg&h=bc0355d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「聖經文獻」可以定義為希伯來聖經正典，即係我哋新教徒嘅舊約。死海古卷入面嘅希伯來聖經抄本數量大概有二百份。除咗以斯帖記之外，其餘嘅舊約書卷都搵得到，當中佔較多嘅係詩篇丶申命記同以賽亞書。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ADqWXxB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FADqWXxB.png&h=edcb36a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「經外文獻」包括稱為舊約次經或偽經嘅文獻丶規章丶律例討論丶釋經書丶詩章丶禱文丶智訓同天啟文獻等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQgrAjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQgrAjB.jpg&h=da4b7f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺所有出土嘅「聖經文獻」當中，最震撼嘅就係1號洞穴發現嘅以賽亞書古卷，可以追溯到公元前125年，亦即係耶穌出世之前一個世紀多。喺呢份古卷出土之前，我哋擁有嘅完整以賽亞書只能夠追溯到公元1008年，意思即係，因為呢個發現，可追溯日期就推前咗成千年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/momWc6r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmomWc6r.jpg&h=29ec7146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以我哋或者會問，既然有公元前嘅抄本，又有1000年之後嘅抄本，咁兩者相似度有幾多呢？兩者幾乎係一致嘅，只有少數嘅文法錯誤或者係串錯字，而呢啲都係可以理解嘅，畢竟呢一千年間都係靠手抄傳遞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YowOOFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYowOOFv.png&h=3599bc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣亦都顯示出，嗰啲古代猶太文士，喺抄寫神話語嘅時候係幾咁細心同精準。而因為咁，我哋手上嘅聖經，尤其係舊約聖經，抄寫者係冇亂咁改動內容，死海古卷係我哋能夠相信舊約聖經嘅其中一個重要證據，知道當中嘅信息冇更改過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwCBXyW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwCBXyW.png&h=30d9dbc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完。"},{"pid":"2fd4013e5dd65c8bd644bc1289cd68494109685a","tid":2253865,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:35:43.000Z","msg":"基督教信仰分享頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gospelsharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgospelsharing&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPY093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=b318f0a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gospelsharing</a>"},{"pid":"7f1fdbfc096f4c5735b5794842b02c7e560fe3b2","tid":2253865,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"事實證明 有啲次經的確係正經 有晒希伯來文"},{"pid":"86e5511e9e6937ba510880257dd7dfeb5b7e6787","tid":2253865,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1fdbfc096f4c5735b5794842b02c7e560fe3b2","tid":2253865,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"事實證明 有啲次經的確係正經 有晒希伯來文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"證明所謂嘅次經 <br />\n其實只係唔符合現代基督宗教嘅narrative而被訂為次經<br />\n到最尾都係啲人想個故事係點就點"},{"pid":"16d667c353fd892acd1cc811b288dd21fab90c12","tid":2253865,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86e5511e9e6937ba510880257dd7dfeb5b7e6787","tid":2253865,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1fdbfc096f4c5735b5794842b02c7e560fe3b2","tid":2253865,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"事實證明 有啲次經的確係正經 有晒希伯來文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"證明所謂嘅次經 <br />\n其實只係唔符合現代基督宗教嘅narrative而被訂為次經<br />\n到最尾都係啲人想個故事係點就點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"睇到中間已經覺得鬼鬼地 原來係Christian channel 🙏🏻"},{"pid":"b89f111ba4291b8eca9a5ea55ea5acfab8fc198c","tid":2253865,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16d667c353fd892acd1cc811b288dd21fab90c12","tid":2253865,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"86e5511e9e6937ba510880257dd7dfeb5b7e6787","tid":2253865,"uid":73404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1fdbfc096f4c5735b5794842b02c7e560fe3b2","tid":2253865,"uid":76710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"事實證明 有啲次經的確係正經 有晒希伯來文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"證明所謂嘅次經 <br />\n其實只係唔符合現代基督宗教嘅narrative而被訂為次經<br />\n到最尾都係啲人想個故事係點就點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:49:53.000Z","msg":"睇到中間已經覺得鬼鬼地 原來係Christian channel 🙏🏻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"我基督徒梗係企喺基督徒立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkg